About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: The Conjuring: Last Rites | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Discover why this case ended it all. #TheConjuring: Last Rites - Only in Theaters September 5.

From New Line Cinema comes the ninth entry in the more than $2 billion theatrical Conjuring universe, The Conjuring: Last Rites, directed by franchise veteran Michael Chaves and produced by franchise architects James Wan and Peter Safran.

The Conjuring: Last Rites delivers another thrilling chapter of the iconic Conjuring cinematic universe, based on real events.  Vera Farmiga and Patrick Wilson reunite for one last case as renowned, real-life paranormal investigators Ed and Lorraine Warren in a powerful and spine-chilling addition to the global box office-breaking franchise.

Farmiga and Wilson star alongside Mia Tomlinson and Ben Hardy, who portray Ed and Lorraine‚Äôs daughter Judy Warren and her boyfriend, Tony Spera, as well as Steve Coulter returning as Father Gordon, Rebecca Calder, Elliot Cowan, K√≠la Lord Cassidy, Beau Gadsdon, John Brotherton and Shannon Kook.

Chaves directs from a screenplay by Ian Goldberg & Richard Naing and David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, story by David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick & James Wan, based on characters created by Chad Hayes & Carey W. Hayes.  The executive producers are Michael Clear, Judson Scott, Hans Ritter, David Leslie Johnson-McGoldrick, Natalia Safran, John Rickard and Michael Chaves.

Chaves is joined behind the camera by his creative team, including director of photography Eli Born, production designer John Frankish, editors Elliot Greenberg and Gregory Plotkin, visual effects supervisor Scott Edelstein, visual effects producer Eric Bruneau and costume designer Graham Churchyard, with casting by Rose Wicksteed and Sophie Kingston-Smith.  The music supervisor is Ian Broucek and the music is by composer Benjamin Wallfisch.

New Line Cinema Presents The Safran Company / An Atomic Monster Production, The Conjuring: Last Rites.  The film will be released worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures and will be only in theaters and IMAX¬Æ in North America on September 5, 2025, and internationally beginning 3 September 2025.

From Sony Pictures Animation, the studio behind Spider-Man: Across the Spider-Verse, comes GOAT, an original action-comedy set in an all-animal world. The story follows Will, a small goat with big dreams who gets a once-in-a-lifetime shot to join the pros and play roarball ‚Äì a high-intensity, co-ed, full-contact sport dominated by the fastest, fiercest animals in the world. Will‚Äôs new teammates aren‚Äôt thrilled about having a little goat on their roster, but Will is determined to revolutionize the sport and prove once and for all that ‚Äúsmalls can ball!‚Äù

For example, a comedy can be transformed into a thriller, or different movies can be combined to create a crossover that doesn‚Äôt exist. These edits allow fans to see their favorite actors and films in a whole new light.
By mixing and re-editing scenes, I aim to build excitement for upcoming releases, highlight unique ideas, and bring cinematic "what-if" scenarios to life. Since these are creative remixes, they may be protected under fair use.

snippet.description:
#jaani  #filhall #akshaykumar #bpraak  
Have you ever selflessly loved someone so much that just their smile can brighten up your day? 

FILHALL, a feel good song about love and it‚Äôs beauty of never giving up. 

From the makers of iconic songs like Qismat , Maan Bhariya , Pachtaoge  and Coka , one of bollywood most celebrated Artist Akshay Kumar  Featuring Nupur sanon , bring to you, their first ever debut Music video , in the voice of Bpraak . The video , shot is done by the concept king Arvindr Khaira  and penned down by one and only lyrical machine JAANI . Filhaal, a song that depicts the story of that true love which is pious, selfless yet incomplete.

Step back in time and relive the golden era of Bollywood with Kishore Kumar's rare gem "Saiyaara" (1980). This soulful melody captures the essence of vintage romance, timeless lyrics, and the golden voice of Kishore Da that still resonates in every heart.

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

Saiyaara tu toh badla nahin hai
Mausam zara sa rootha hua hai

[Bridge]
Jis roz hum tum phir se milenge
Yeh saari baatein tujhse kahenge

Duniya mein chaahe ban jaayein jo bhi

Haaye main mar hi jaaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Jo tujhko na paaun
Main mar hi jaaun

Honthon pe lamha lamha
Hai naam tera haaye
Tujhko hi gaaun main, tujhko pukaaroon

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

snippet.title: Esports World Cup 2025 Day 3 | Magnus vs Nihal | Arjun Erigaisi vs Nepo | Hindi commentary
snippet.description:
The E-sports world cup 2025 begins on 29th July and goes on until 1st of August 2025. It's a 16-player event with some of the biggest names in the world of chess! 

The commentary will be in Hinglish. Watch on Sony Liv without 7 minutes delay: https://www.sonyliv.com/live-sport/e-sports-world-cup-2025-1790006658/esports-chess-at-ewc-25-quarter-finals-semi-finals-31-jul-2025-1090485747?watch=true

Let's try and understand the format:
16 players are segregated in group of 4 players. So there are 4 groups in all. The time control is 10+0. 
On day 1 we had 4 players who topped the 4 groups and will have a rest day on 30th of July 2025.

The players who topped are: 
A group - Levon Aronian
B group - Arjun Erigaisi
C group - Alireza Firouzja
D group - Magnus Carlsen

On day 2 we had 4 more players who joined them:
A group - Ian Nepomniachtchi
B group - Nihal Sarin
C group - Hikaru Nakamura
D group - Nodirbek Abdusattorov

It's now time for Quarter Finals and Semi Finals:
Arjun Erigaisi vs Ian Nepomniachtchi
Nodirbek Abdusattorov vs Alireza Firouzja
Magnus Carlsen vs Nihal Sarin
Hikaru Nakamura vs Levon Aronian

QF: Best of 4 games with a time control of 10+0 followed by Armageddon. 
SF: Best of 6 games with a time control of 10+0 followed by Armageddon

Articles on ChessBase India by Shahid Ahmed:
Day 1: https://chessbase.in/news/Esports-World-Cup-2025-Main-Event-Day-1-report
Day 2: https://chessbase.in/news/Esports-World-Cup-2025-Main-Event-Day-2-report

snippet.title: [EN] 2025 PMWC at EWC Survival Stage D2 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
SURVIVAL STAGE DAY 2 | JULY 30

The 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP continues with the final day of the Survival Stage in Riyadh! The battle reaches its climax as teams fight for their last chance to reach the Grand Finals and claim their share of the massive $3,000,000 prize pool.

Today is the day‚Äîonly 8 teams will survive and secure the final spots in the Grand Finals. After an intense Group Stage and Day 1 of the Survival Stage, the pressure is at an all-time high. Every moment counts, every zone matters, and only the strongest will advance.

The Survival Stage is where stories are rewritten and underdogs can rise. With limited spots left, this is the moment to BEAT THE HEAT or go home. 

üî•How does SMASH RULE work in Grand Finals? 
After Day 2 of Grand Finals, the Match Point Threshold will be set to the #1 ranked team‚Äôs points +10. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals‚Äîwinning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn‚Äôt bring the championship. If no team secures the title via SMASH Rule by Match 18, the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

üî• Why You Can‚Äôt Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
- The top 16 teams on one stage ‚Äî no second chances!
- Every match counts in the race for the championship!
- Witness PUBG MOBILE history in the making!
- Explosive SMASH RULE format ‚Äî pressure-packed, winner-takes-all action!

Group Stage: July 25‚Äì27

Grand Finals: August 1‚Äì3

Lyrics :

haye jaatan paatan piche shad jaou 
apni ishq kahani haye tera milna adan c menu jeyo peyase nu paani , ho na tu dekhi gareebi meri na oudeya sadhaa cehara han m duniya jittni cahouna aw ni par hath fadke teraa,

haye ave kahton khud nu tu samjde kalla tere nal modha lake khadugi , 
jitt leya ge apan dove duniya sari nu , bhave rabb aje tahvi adugiii , 
duniya kihanu a athe khush dekh k tu gall dil te kyu lake bath dai 

khadi aw main end tak jatta tere nal ave dhareyan kyu dhaa k bath dai 

ik tan rakane ashi marte gareebi ne te outo kismat madi ae 
ounj menu sareyan ne apna keha ja ghumi pith picho vaji tadi ae , 
chitt kare khake salfas marja 
ni hunde bebe bappu tang dekh k 
 
kade kade man ja kharab ho janda ni saleya duniya de rang dekh k 

shad di ni hath tera door nayeo hundi ave firda kyu ae das dolda , 
outhke tere layi kara nitt ardaasa jado guru ghar pathi hunda bolda , 
time timu changa mada ape lang jana , 
kalla shad di ni kade tere nal aw ve , duneya jittugi hath fad k main tera pith lagan ni dindi teri yaara  ve,
socha vich pendi aw rakan yaara odo jado kalla kite jake bath dai

bhuldi ni tenu main mandaur waleya ve inna mada nayeo meda a rakaan da, 
ni dar lage menu sala duniyadari da ounj tenu tan main changi tara jaanda, 
han laiju shavy sheti pr main karake tenu,
main airport outte rona gal nal lake tenu,
jado kite menu channa miss wahla kre, ni gaane sabbe de fer lake bath dai,
haye khadi aw main end tak jatta tere nal, ave dhareyan kyu dhaa k bath dai 

ho naal khan wale hi oudaoune ne majak , bhed gair thodi hunde das kholde ,
dukh tan rakane sala odo vad hunda jado apne e pith piche bolde

tenu v hona a mere payar outte maan , tere naam nal ganeya nu bharju,
rabb nalo vadd menu maan aw tere te hath shad jai na ose tha te marju

hassa aounda handeya loka de muha te dil luttan de dhang dekh k
